animeTitle: My Wife Is Actually the Empress?
otherNames: My Wife Is Actually the Empress?, My Wife Is Actually the Emperor, My Wife Is Actually the Emperor, Wǒ Jiā Niángzǐ Jìngrán Shì Nǚ Dì?, 我家娘子竟然是女帝？
synopsis: With my wife's breathtaking beauty, not even the newly enthroned empress can match her! With my wife's marvelous culinary skills, not even the empress's royal chefs can match her! My wife loves me and cares about me very very much, and I wouldn't trade her for even the empress! Wait, what? My wife is the empress?!
